## One Note — pydantic Version
The plan specified `pydantic==2.7.0`, but `pydantic-core 2.18.1` (its dependency) has no pre-built wheel for Python 3.13 on Windows and requires Rust to compile, which failed. Bumped to `pydantic==2.8.2` (ships `pydantic-core 2.20.1` with a Win/Py3.13 wheel). This is a patch-safe bump — **no API changes, same Pydantic v2 semantics**.

